thread.title: Vicki Clark
thread.title_full: Trade Tested reviewed by Vicki Clark

author: Vicki Clark
title: Vicki Clark
text:
: “I have only had these 4 planters for a short time - but they are already full of soil and half are planted up with green leafy veggies.They were simple to assemble and light to move into place - and It certainly makes tending my veggie patch much easier! So I can say yes - I am pleased with my purchase.”
V. A. Clark
